{"tid":1515290,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有關陳秋實律師的報平安 （內有簡體字慎入）","createTime":"2019-08-29T05:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T07:55:53.000Z","uid":186908,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c936122b136de58105d2b3533f95422f15ab1c8c","tid":1515290,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"話說近排轉twitter sd文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有好多中國人係正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />勁多反共<br />\n<br />\n咁我前日見到依張weibo冇曬野既相就開post 話佢已經被消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/49vrQvb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F49vrQvb.png&h=302daf67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有幾十個人rt左<br />\n直到琴日夜晚有人話佢冇事 我話可能係假報平安呢 <br />\n佢就比左佢地既對話我睇 話暫時冇事 佢依家要好低調，每日都有佢消息，重話佢依家係到練字，避風頭火勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以下三張圖為對話記錄。黑格我打既 保障返佢個人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBDQxKR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBDQxKR.png&h=5e5fa3c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B4Ht3Ry.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB4Ht3Ry.png&h=5bdf322c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/29/124716_297b7ce89e9e40032fb1b0411de2cf39.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F29%2F124716_297b7ce89e9e40032fb1b0411de2cf39.png&h=385c4367&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但其他所有acc都被人del曬<br />\n咁我就話香港人好擔心佢 今朝起身就收到依張<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/czVLmMX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FczVLmMX.png&h=da27fbb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民佢話依家風頭火勢唔會咁快消失 係驚之後靜左之後會被消失（中共一貫做法）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n題外話 起身佢問我<span style=\"color: red;\"> [sorry 我真係唔識睇簡體搞到我唔識覆］</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 驻港恶狗凌晨&ldquo;换班&rdquo;入港了？？只进不出？？是否如此？<br />\n<br />\n我覆佢話差唔多全部都係武警嚟㗎啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： 大家要集思广益，想应对办法！这很有可能对着，九月二号，九月三号去，换防。是一个堂而皇之的。借口吧，这几天，入驻的驻扎。而该换防出来的，会用交接事宜。没弄好，而不出港。就为下月那两天的事情！<br />\n<br />\n我問佢： 您們看到有一班武警換班？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：看到的是军车入港！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9gyvKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9gyvKE.jpg&h=c49bd27e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GKpTvKE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGKpTvKE.jpg&h=014e4c3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重有條片點扔上黎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 他们换防不怕，就怕，进去以交接等事宜没处理好，不出来。毕竟九月二号，九月三号，临近<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 同胞们现在首要任务是，集思广益。应对，入军对策。必须想好各种预案！以便有备无患！少受伤，少流血<br />\n<br />\n佢話連午間新聞都講緊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XRmR1R2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXRmR1R2.jpg&h=a2683ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u05O35u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu05O35u.jpg&h=f6e30bb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 他们换防我不担心的，因为每年一次，这算常规，我担心的是，他们要是以交接事宜没处理好，该出来的不出来，因为马上就到九月二号三好了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 假途灭虢之计<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/igSJSZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FigSJSZc.jpg&h=908c80db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人知點覆？我真係唔太識簡體"},{"pid":"478db9f4bea11ce8ae83f4b6dfa513744248b54d","tid":1515290,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"唔好吊我話全部簡體字"},{"pid":"ccd60f0740267b1ba2fbe797fdb251386cc9fcb8","tid":1515290,"uid":100406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:39:30.000Z","msg":"數字終於郁了<br />\nWhite House Petitions 回來了！可惜反對曾偉雄的聯署過了截止日期一日！令到舊聯署唔到數!<br />\n<br />\n請各兄弟重新簽署以下這個聯署！香港人心不死！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRn4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=942f3415\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-demand-rejection-andy-tsangs-nomination-united-nations-positions-re-petition</a>"},{"pid":"af3a6b0d99277aa6adb22cfda5d789a6793ac0a7","tid":1515290,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:39:49.000Z","msg":"得閒既話勇武巴睇下<br />\n[勇武手足入］水炮車受害人Dietrich Wagner警戒世人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1512162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1512162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1bee6373e3cc54591a1da1a41a63a338d47ceb2f","tid":1515290,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ccd60f0740267b1ba2fbe797fdb25